creator: Oliver Herford
description:
LibriVox recording of The Kitten's Garden of Verses by Oliver Herford.

Read in English by Rachel.

The Kitten's Garden of Verses is a book of short poetry, in the style of Robert Louis Stevenson's A Child's Garden of Verses. Many of the poems have similar titles to poems in A Child's Garden of Verses. Summary by Summary by Rachel.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
